{
  "stem": "20405.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, it was not so easy to take them out either because they were all on the bended knees and heads, because they were like sardines inside.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very difficult to pick them up out. with a-- with a cane getting from the head and push them out or with belts, tied them up in one hand, and push them out again.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's the only way we could take the dead bodies from the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And was funny and the cars jumping when the car was coming with the gas, they had a-- a Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah-- yeah it was gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ventilation, ventilation, because the guys want to-- it was to take them out at three, four minutes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ventilation, was nothing, and we were not going right away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember one day, three Germans SS girls came in with some officers, SS officers, no.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the transport just came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody was inside dying with the gas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And those three girls from their SS went from the little window, was a little windows on the doors, like they had on the ships, those kind of windows, looking out the window, out.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were looking out the-- those people, they were dying, and they were laughing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were laughing something unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How could women, girls, could see such a thing and laughing?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were so much brainwashed from that-- I don't want to say the word-- that Hitler, that animal.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Now, what were they doing with like this?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the crematoria-- I don't remember if it were two or three, it doesn't matter which one it was it-- was three French guys, Jewish.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were specialists in gold.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
